```plantuml
@startuml DevOps-Represent_devopsgirls-bootcamp-cn-2
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "User"

package "Frontend (React SPA)" {
  rectangle "UI Components" as ReactUI
  rectangle "Client.js" as ClientJS
  rectangle "Render.js" as RenderJS
  rectangle "Config.js" as ConfigJS
}

package "AWS Infrastructure" {
  rectangle "S3 Bucket\nStatic Hosting" as S3Bucket #orange
  rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGateway #lightblue
  rectangle "Lambda Function" as Lambda #yellow
  database "DynamoDB\n(NoSQL)" as DynamoDB #lightgreen
}

User --> ReactUI
ReactUI --> S3Bucket
ReactUI --> APIGateway

APIGateway --> Lambda
Lambda --> DynamoDB

note right of APIGateway
  Proxy pattern (/{proxy+})
end note

note right of Lambda
  Handles CRUD operations
  Interacts with DynamoDB
end note

note bottom of DynamoDB
  Stores todo items
end note

note top of S3Bucket
  Hosts React SPA
end note
@enduml
```